{"tid":10151,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"中文作文點先作得好？","createTime":"2016-11-28T23:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T10:16:34.000Z","uid":27196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f3b10eaea5cd6bc1a067f9104538ba966b5b9ff","tid":10151,"uid":27196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T23:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e98b44b99758df446f501a32503d8f8cafc6f4","tid":10151,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T02:11:36.000Z","msg":"老生常談，多睇"},{"pid":"7e1bfeb0ded5a679a45fd181cb540bd0f9d3329a","tid":10151,"uid":23701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:57:58.000Z","msg":"巴打可唔可以講多啲<br />\n係記抒描定係論說文<br />\n淨係放低幾隻好難答喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e8df1380a8c9d213b5bf219430fdf72816fbc6","tid":10151,"uid":27196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打可唔可以講多啲<br />\n係記抒描定係論說文<br />\n淨係放低幾隻好難答喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry <br />\n抒情文"},{"pid":"50e7f72fc93011f817032a79db6af16ff9a1b080","tid":10151,"uid":32834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:05:29.000Z","msg":"扼要地講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記住一樣野，唔好將情感直接寫出黎，例如你難過，就唔好寫「我心裡覺得難過」。<br />\n所有出色既抒情一定要透過寫景、物、事來表達，（即係所謂間接抒情），如果你可以透過寫景物事，唔直接寫你情感而令情感從中顯露，就叫做好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e48039ddc6a4fa0bea95e11f9770506806d73d","tid":10151,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"作文可以練<br />\n文學創作就比較唔同<br />\n推薦 王鼎鈞 作文六法<br />\n佢係台灣散文大家黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085efb40961fe8cc2b3800c22b5cd308e2c3138e","tid":10151,"uid":38050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:45:01.000Z","msg":"記敍抒情有完整結構，<br />\n起碼做好起承轉合同反思，<br />\n諗定部分情節係腦度隨時攞黎用，<br />\n最後一定要寫，一定要寫，一定要寫，<br />\npractice make perfect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3274209b43627e107c23a107d2599b4df64cfa5","tid":10151,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:11:54.000Z","msg":"用字方面用少d「我」、「的」、「是」呢類字，字句盡量簡潔<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n「我的哥哥是一個很煩的人。」<br />\n更正：<br />\n「哥哥很煩。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然以上例子係最低級"},{"pid":"244c1031f4ddb0e5f2d7c77f8dcb9b2dd97912a4","tid":10151,"uid":33784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:15:33.000Z","msg":"擦多啲中文老師鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0cbeca3ec34567adcb8ec4cc20e96ae9a31df1","tid":10151,"uid":4955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:16:34.000Z","msg":"dse作文就係扣題"}]}